{
  "stem": "26486.5",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then the appell was only one day, instead of three.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Oh, I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they-- they started by coming and telling you, you don't have to go to work today.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You can stay there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We knew there was something going on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We knew Roosevelt had done something good for us, for everybody.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[DRINKS] Excuse me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So from that time on, as I said, the Red Cross was coming, little more frequent-- frequently.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they would bring vitamin pills, which we never saw either.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They would take them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But the Germans took them for them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The officer [INAUDIBLE] and the-- you know, the officers keep them for their families, not for us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But anyway, we didn't care.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We said, as long as they're bringing stuff in, that's good sign.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
